; RISK: • More visually cluttered interface for inexperienced users.
; RISK: • No impact on stability or security.
; NOTE: Power-user/transparency setting: Use with caution on system components.
; RESTART: EXPLORER
"Hidden"=dword:00000001
"ShowSuperHidden"=dword:00000001

