; IMPACT: • Reduces the visible activity history.
; RISK: • Loss of a convenient feature (recent items per application).
; RISK: • No system risk.
; NOTE: Privacy setting + clean menu: perfect for removing recent items everywhere and keeping Windows minimal.
; RESTART: EXPLORER
[HKEY_CURRENT_USER\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Explorer\Advanced]
"Start_JumpListItems"=dword:00000000

; KORSiOS - [Explorer / UI]• History • Disable "Recent Files" + "Recent Documents" history
; ID: Explorer_DisableRecentFiles
