; RISK: • Loss of visual comfort (animations, aesthetic effects).
; RISK: • No impact on stability, security, or basic functionality.
; NOTE: Performance/UI simplicity setting: prioritizes speed over aesthetics.
; RESTART: EXPLORER
[HKEY_CURRENT_USER\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Explorer\VisualEffects]
"VisualFXSetting"=dword:00000002

