; KORSiOS - [Explorer / UI]• Responsiveness • Disable Windows Animations
; ID: Explorer_DisableWindowsAnimations
; DESC: Disables window minimize/restore animations.
; IMPACT: • Removes animation when minimizing/restored windows.
