; KORSiOS - [Explorer / UI]• History • Disable automatic suggestions in the address bar (AutoSuggest)
; ID: Explorer_DisableAutoSuggest
; DESC: Disables automatic suggestions when typing in the address bar and certain Explorer fields.
; IMPACT: • Disables autosuggest when you type a path in the Explorer address bar.
; IMPACT: • Reduces suggestions based on history (paths, folders, recent locations).
; IMPACT: • Limits the display of potentially private items while typing (shared PC / streaming).
; RISK: • Reduced convenience: less help in quickly finding previously used folders.
; RISK: • Does not necessarily disable all Windows suggestions (e.g., Start, Run search, etc.).
; RISK: • No impact on stability or security.
