; ID: Explorer_DisablePreviewHandlers
; DESC: Disables built-in Preview Handlers in Explorer.
; IMPACT: • Disables the display of previews in the Preview pane (PDFs, images, documents, etc.).
; IMPACT: • Reduces certain COM overhead/extensions related to previews.
; IMPACT: • May improve stability and prevent slowdowns in certain folders.
; RISK: • You lose the Preview pane in Explorer.
