; IMPACT: - “Back up your files”
; IMPACT: - Cloud notifications in Windows Explorer
; RISK: • You will no longer see certain OneDrive reminders (which is often the intended purpose).
; RISK: • No system risk.
; NOTE: Anti-ad setting / Explorer clean: excellent safe tweak to remove OneDrive pop-ups and keep Windows minimal.
