; IMPACT: • Visual notifications remain displayed, but without audible alerts.
; RISK: • Missed audible alerts (messages, reminders, important events).
; RISK: • No impact on stability, security, or performance.
; NOTE: Comfort/Silent setting: Makes the system quieter while retaining visual notifications.
