; DESC: Disables "tips," "recommendations," and Windows suggestions notifications.
; IMPACT: • Reduces intrusive pop-ups (e.g., Microsoft recommendations, features to enable, etc.).
; IMPACT: • Makes the experience quieter and more "professional."
; RISK: • May miss some useful tips for new users.
; RISK: • No risk to stability or security.
; NOTE: Anti-nagging/pro-clean setting: a very good tweak for a minimal Windows system, especially for gaming or workstation setups.
